SAND POINT GRAVEL CO., Appellant, v. UNITED STATES EMPLOYEES’ COMPENSATION COMMISSION et al., Appellees. No. 6002. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. March 7, 1930.

Before DIETRICH and WILBUR, Circuit Judges, and KERRIGAN, District •Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Dismissed upon motion of appellees for failure of appellant to print record.
